==Translingual==

===Pronunciation===
/ xə / the voiceless velar fricative as the ending of the German doch. Many Hindi speakers will incorrectly pronounce it as / k<sup>h</sup>ə / ([[ख]]) instead.

===Letter===
'''ख़''' (<u>kh</u>)

#Consonant of the [[Devanagari]] script. It is not included in the traditional alphabet as it represents a sound borrowed from [[Persian]], but is sometimes alphabetized just after [[ख]].

